mention Liverpool\'s prolific strikeforce of Luis Suarez and Daniel Sturridge.</font></p>\n<div class=\"clear\"> </div>\n<div class=\"artSplitter\"> <img alt=\"Crocked: Man City captain Vincent Kompany limps out of training after a collision with Micah Richards\" class=\"blkBorder img-share\" height=\"525\" id=\"i-a78d0e5d\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/12/article-2603173-1D0D573700000578-248_634x525.jpg\" width=\"634\"/> <p class=\"imageCaption\">Crocked: Man City captain Vincent Kompany limps out of training after a collision with Micah Richards</p> </div>\n<p> </p>\n<div class=\"clear\"> </div>\n<div class=\"artSplitter\"> <img alt=\"Painful: Both Kompany (left) and Micah Richards lie on the floor after their mid-air collision in training\" class=\"blkBorder img-share\" height=\"469\" id=\"i-9aa70e32\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/12/article-2603173-1D0D578500000578-18_634x469.jpg\" width=\"634\"/> <p class=\"imageCaption\">Painful: Both Kompany (left) and Micah Richards lie on the floor after their mid-air collision in training</p><div class=\"moduleFull\"> <a class=\"namedLink\" name=\"video\"></a><div class=\"item\"> <div id=\"v-3460793165001\" style=\"width:636px;\"> <div class=\"videoplayer-large\" style=\"overflow-y:hidden\"> <a> <div class=\"videoplayer-title-bg\"></div> <div class=\"videoplayer-title\">Pellegrini: An excess of anxiety could mean more mistakes</div> <div class=\"btnBg\"></div> <span class=\"playbtn\"></span> <center> <img class=\"plcHlder\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/12/video-undefined-1D0D86B700000578-849_636x358.jpg\"/> </center> </a> </div> <div class=\"sport\"> <div class=\"wocc videoplayer-keyline\"></div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>\n<p> </p>\n<p><font style=\"font-size: 1.2em;\">The Uruguayan has already notched 29 Premier League this season, while Sturridge has 20, and they\'ll fancy their chances of adding to that should Kompany miss tomorrow\'s clash.</font></p>\n<p><font style=\"font-size: 1.2em;\">Martin Demichelis would have been expected to line up alongside Kompany at the heart of the City defence. But should Kompany fail to recover, then either Joleon Lescott or Javi Garcia will most likely deputise.</font></p>\n<p></p>\n<div class=\"relatedItemsTopBorder\"> </div>\n<div class=\"relatedItems\"> <h4>More...</h4> <ul> <li><a href=\"/sport/football/article-2601458/LIVERPOOL-vs-MANCHESTER-CITY-All-latest-team-news-stats-crunch-battle-race-Premier-League-title.html\"> LIVERPOOL vs MANCHESTER CITY: All the latest team news and stats for the crunch battle in race for Premier League title</a></li> <li><a href=\"/sport/football/article-2603124/Vincent-Kompany-confident-Liverpool-battle-ahead-Premier-League-title-decider.html\"> Liverpool boss Rodgers demands midfield dominance ahead of Premier League title decider against City</a></li> <li><a href=\"/sport/football/article-2603112/Vincent-Kompany-insists-Manchester-City-wont-daunted-Liverpool-Anfield-Premier-League-title-showdown.html\"> Kompany won\'t be fazed by Liverpool as Man City aim to strike killer blow in Premier League title race at Anfield</a></li> <li><a href=\"/sport/football/article-2602794/It-feels-just-like-1980s-But-glory-days-finally-return-Anfield.html\"> Rodgers\' rampant Liverpool feel just like the legendary 1980s sides... but will the glory days finally return to Anfield?</a></li> <li><a href=\"/sport/football/article-2598043/Liverpool-vs-Man-City-THE-match-decide-destination-Premier-League-title.html\"> Liverpool vs Man City is THE match to decide destination of the Premier League title... but will it live up to these classics?</a></li> <li><a href=\"/sport/football/article-2597747/Vincent-Kompany-confidence-victory-Southampton-ahead-Liverpool-Premier-League-title-clash.html\"> Kompany full of confidence after victory over Saints ahead of Reds title clash</a></li> </ul> </div>\n<div class=\"clear\"> </div>\n<div class=\"artSplitter\"> <img alt=\"Up you come: Yaya Toure (right) helps Kompany up of the floor after the defender is injured in training\" class=\"blkBorder img-share\" height=\"464\" id=\"i-a7ce0e63\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/12/article-2603173-1D0D574500000578-766_634x464.jpg\" width=\"634\"/> <p class=\"imageCaption\">Up you come: Yaya Toure (right) helps Kompany up of the floor after the defender is injured in training</p> </div>\n<p> </p>\n<div class=\"clear\"> </div>\n<p><font style=\"font-size:1.2em;\">The incident on the training ground looked innocuous as Kompany and Richards challenged for a high ball, but the Belgian international looked to land awkwardly and was said to let out a loud cry in pain.</font></p>\n<p><font style=\"font-size:1.2em;\">His concerned team-mates were quick to rush to his aid as he clutched his left knee, with Yaya Toure helping the City captain up off the ground.</font></p>\n<p><font style=\"font-size:1.2em;\">Samir Nasri then helped Kompany off the training ground.<br/></font></p>\n<p><font style=\"font-size:1.2em;\">Third-placed City are four points behind league leaders Liverpool with two games in hand. But were the Reds to win tomorrow, even victory in their two extra matches would still leave City a point behind Brendan Rodgers\' men.</font></p>\n<div class=\"clear\"> </div>\n<div class=\"artSplitter\"> <img alt=\"In form: Daniel Sturridge (left) and Luis Suarez have been scoring freely for Liverpool this season\" class=\"blkBorder img-share\" height=\"375\" id=\"i-a8d60e69\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/12/article-2603173-1CB24D5700000578-190_634x375.jpg\" width=\"634\"/> <p class=\"imageCaption\">In form: Daniel Sturridge (left) and Luis Suarez have been scoring freely for Liverpool this season</p><div class=\"moduleFull\"> <div class=\"item\"> <div id=\"v-3356747189001\" style=\"width:636px;\"> <div class=\"videoplayer-large\" style=\"overflow-y:hidden\"> <a> <div class=\"videoplayer-title-bg\"></div> <div class=\"videoplayer-title\">Fun