.jpg\" width=\"634\"/> <p class=\"imageCaption\">Hair down: Fabregas (right) and Sergio Busquets (left) fish something out of the water</p> </div>\n<p> </p>\n<p><font style=\"font-size:1.2em;\">Barcelona were dumped out of the Champions League on Wednesday night after a 1-0 loss to Atletico Madrid (2-1 on agg).</font></p>\n<p><font style=\"font-size:1.2em;\">It is now time to focus on their domestic efforts, with a league fixture away at Granada on Saturday.</font></p>\n<p><font style=\"font-size:1.2em;\">Carles Puyol and Xavi were also at the party ahead of the game, and Tata Martino is sure to have put them through their paces following the midweek defeat.</font></p>\n<div class=\"clear\"> </div>\n<div class=\"artSplitter\"> <img alt=\"Arrival: Sergio Busquets turns up with his partner to the Fabregas bash\" class=\"blkBorder img-share\" height=\"413\" id=\"i-a5730e4a\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/11/article-2602734-1D02460800000578-866_634x413.jpg\" width=\"634\"/> <p class=\"imageCaption\">Arrival: Sergio Busquets turns up with his partner to the Fabregas bash</p> </div>\n<p> </p>\n<div class=\"clear\"> </div>\n<div class=\"artSplitter\"> <img alt=\"Celebrate: Midfielder Xavi with his partner at Fabregas\' daughter\'s first birthday party\" class=\"blkBorder img-share\" height=\"825\" id=\"i-a78d0e65\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/11/article-2602734-1D02349E00000578-984_634x825.jpg\" width=\"634\"/> <p class=\"imageCaption\">Celebrate: Midfielder Xavi with his partner at Fabregas\' daughter\'s first birthday party</p><div class=\"moduleFull\"> <div class=\"item\"> <div id=\"v-2545380526001\" style=\"width:636px;\"> <div class=\"videoplayer-large\" style=\"overflow-y:hidden\"> <a> <div class=\"videoplayer-title-bg\"></div> <div class=\"videoplayer-title\">BARCELONA WEDDING Xavi gets married</div> <div class=\"btnBg\"></div> <span class=\"playbtn\"></span> <center> <img class=\"plcHlder\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2013/07/15/video-undefined-1AD22DE6000005DC-204_292x165.jpg\"/> </center> </a> </div> <div class=\"sport\"> <div class=\"wocc videoplayer-keyline\"></div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>\n<p> </p>\n<div class=\"clear\"> </div>\n<div class=\"artSplitter\"> <img alt=\"Down and out: Barcelona were eliminated from the Champions League by Atletico Madrid in the week\" class=\"blkBorder img-share\" height=\"438\" id=\"i-a46d0e40\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/11/article-2602734-1D01670000000578-441_634x438.jpg\" width=\"634\"/> <p class=\"imageCaption\">Down and out: Barcelona were eliminated from the Champions League by Atletico Madrid in the week</p><div class=\"moduleFull\"> <div class=\"item\"> <div id=\"v-3447999462001\" style=\"width:636px;\"> <div class=\"videoplayer-large\" style=\"overflow-y:hidden\"> <a> <div class=\"videoplayer-title-bg\"></div> <div class=\"videoplayer-title\">Neymar gets nutmegged by freestyler Séan Garnier at Castol shoot</div> <div class=\"btnBg\"></div> <span class=\"playbtn\"></span> <center> <img class=\"plcHlder\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/09/video-undefined-1CF4F31100000578-121_636x358.jpg\"/> </center> </a> </div> <div class=\"sport\"> <div class=\"wocc videoplayer-keyline\"></div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>\n<p> </p>\n<div class=\"relatedItemsTopBorder\"> </div>\n<div class=\"relatedItems\"> <h4>More...</h4> <ul> <li><a href=\"/sport/football/article-2602656/Schalke-0-1-Barcelona-match-report-Munir-El-Haddadi-nets-late-winner-Catalans-set-UEFA-Youth-League-final-against-Benfica.html\"> Schalke 0-1 Barcelona: Top scorer Munir nets late winner as Catalans set up UEFA Youth League final against Benfica</a></li> <li><a href=\"/sport/football/article-2602651/Bale-Modric-Co-lather-new-ad-Real-stars-prepare-close-shave.html\"> Bale, Modric and Co lather up in new ad as Real stars prepare for another close shave</a></li> <li><a href=\"/sport/football/article-2602626/Jose-Mourinho-specialist-winning-Arsenal-laughable-reader-comments-week.html\"> Mourinho is a specialist in winning while Arsenal are just laughable... it\'s the reader comments of the week</a></li> <li><a href=\"/sport/football/article-2602589/The-view-Manchester-Shinji-Kagawa-stay-Manchester-United-thrive-Japan-star.html\"> The view from Manchester: Kagawa must stay! United can thrive with Japan star and Mata at heart of their attack</a></li> <li><a href=\"/sport/football/article-2602488/Real-Madrid-0-4-Benfica-UEFA-Youth-League-semi-final.html\"> Real Madrid 0-4 Benfica: Zidane\'s son taken off as Spanish side are smashed in UEFA Youth League semi-final in Switzerland</a></li> <li><a href=\"/sport/football/article-2602639/EXCLUSIVE-City-axe-academy-chief-Sellars-fears-homegrown-quota-grow.html\"> EXCLUSIVE: Sellars axed from Man City academy role as fears over homegrown quota grow</a></li> </ul> </div>\n<br/>\n<p> </p>\n<div class=\"clear\"> </div>\n<div class=\"column-content cleared\"> <div class=\"shareArticles\"> <h3 class=\"social-links-title\">Share or comment on this article</h3> <div class=\"social-links cleared\" id=\"socialLinks\"> <ul class=\"bigLinks sc-icns cleared\"> <li class=\"facebook\"> <a class=\"js-tl\" onclick=\'postToFB(\"bottom\"); return false;\' rel=\"nofollow\"></a> </li> <li class=\"twitter\"> <a class=\"js-tl\" onclick=\"postToTWTTR(\'bottom\'); return false;\" rel=\"nofollow\"></a> </li> <li class=\"pinterest\"> <a class=\"js-tl\" onclick=\"postToPinterest(\'bottom\'); return false;\" rel=\"nofollow\"></a> </li> <li class=\"googleplus\"> <span class=\"g-interactivepost\" data-calltoactionlabel=\"VIEW\" data-calltoactionurl=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2602734/Barcelona-players-WAGS-attend-Cesc-Fabregas-daughters-birthday.html\" data-clientid=\"746589970956-e10ciaf67a1id9ggu75ph3ds0sthn7j6.apps.googleusercontent.com\" data-contentdeeplinkid=\"/pages\" data-contenturl=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2602734/Barcelona-players-WAGS-attend-Cesc-Fabregas-daughters-birthday.html\" data-cookiepolicy=\"single_host_origin\" data-prefilltext=\"Barca players forget their troubles on the pitch with party for Fabregas\' daughter\"> <a class=\"js-tl\" onclick=\"postToGPlus(\'bottom\');\" rel=\"nofollow\"></a> </span> </li> <li class=\"email\"> <a class=\"js-tl\" href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2602734/emailArticle.html\" onclick=\"emailArticle(\'bottom\');\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_new\" title=\"Email to a friend\"> </a> </li> <li class=\"share\" id=\"shareLinkBottom\"> <a class=\"js-sl share-link\" href=\"#socialLinks\"> </a> </li> <li class=\"social-stats social-stats-pipe\" id=\"shareCountBottom\"> <div> <div class=\"shares_count\">34</div><div class=\"shares_text\">shares</div> </div> </li> <li class=\"add-comment\" id=\"addCommentButton\"> <a href=\"#newcomment\" rel=\"nofollow\"> </a> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div>','http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/11/article-2602734-1D09B3E300000578-482_1024x615_large.jpg',NULL,'2014-04-12 16:57:59','2014-04-12 14:47:29'),(37,'2bea6d8cfcff9277811a95b3e6767036cd3ec8c01fd771449ebf0d3ec4e89722','dailymail',NULL,'LIVE - Real Madrid v Almeria: La Liga','http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2603110/LIVE-Real-Madrid-v-Almeria-La-Liga.html',' By Tom Sheen Follow @@Tom_Sheen Published: 06:12 EST, 12 April 2014 | Updated: 07:08 EST, 12 April 2014 3 View comments REAL MADRID V ALMERIASantiago Bernabeu, MadridLa Liga(Kick-off 9pm BST)  Real Madrid may be in the semi-finals of the Champions League, but they will be looking to get their La Liga campaign back on track at the Bernabeu. A win against Almeria would put Carlo Ancelotti\'s men level on points with their city rivals Atletico, who led the way in Spain coming into the weekend. Real Madrid will also have one eye on their Copa del Rey final against Barcelona at the Mestalla on Wednesday.  Tom Sheen Host commentator Auto-update 22:48 FULL TIME: Real Madrid 4-0 Almeria Real Madrid move into second place in La Liga. They are now level on points with their cross town rivals - and have a superior goal difference - but are second due to the head-to-head record. Diego Simeone\'s men play Getafe tomorrow night. 22:45 89mins Real Madrid fans starting to file out of the Bernabeu. Isco should have sent them on their way with a goal there as well. Benzema turned and found the former Malaga man in the box but he gets his shot all wrong and it dribbles straight into Esteban\'s arms. 22:40 85mins: GOAL! REAL MADRID 4-0 Almeria Lovely pass and a lovely finish to put the icing on Real Madrid\'s cake. Illarramendi lofts a pass to Morata - half of the Almeria defence tries to play offside, the other doesn\'t - and Morata lets the ball bounce once before stroking the ball into the roof of the net, neat finish. Finishing touch: Alvaro Morata makes it 4-0 to Real Madrid with a smart finish 22:38 81mins Terrible miss from Benzema, he\'s had some really good chances tonight. Modric\'s free-kick hits the wall, it falls to Morata who cleverly back-heels to Benzema. Rather than the cool and calm finish we are used to seeing from him, he snatches at it, hitting the ball as hard as he can. It, of course, flies over the top. 22:35 78mins Real Madrid are claiming for a penalty, but I think that would have been harsh had it been given. Isco scoops a clever ball over the top to Morata and the defender doesn\'t get too much of the ball but the substitute definitely tries to make the most of the contact, going down rather too easily. 22:31 75mins Another good chance for Benzema. Morata is set off down the left, he cuts back inside ad curls a ball into the striker, who takes it first time but drags the volley just wide. 22:29 73mins: Real Mdrid sub Fabio Coentrao is replaced by another youngster Diego Llorente. 22:25 70mins: Real Madrid sub Gareth Bale is replaced by Real youngster Alvaro Morata. 22:25 68mins Sustained pressure from Real Madrid and a couple of close calls but they can\'t quite turn the ball into the net. Coentrao fires across the box and then it comes the other way from Isco. 22:21 65mins Diego Lopez is finally called into action and makes a really good save. From the free-kick the big goalkeeper gets down to his left smartly. Game over: Isco adds Real Madrid\'s third and ends the contest 22:20 64mins: Real Madrid sub Angel di Maria is replaced by Casemiro. Excellent performance from the Argentine. 22:16 60mins Esteban goes some way to making up for that earlier miss, with a good save from marauding left back Fabio Coentrao. The overlapping full back had options but decides to shoot through the goalkeeper\'s legs, Esteban gets just enough on it to keep him out. 22:11 56mins: GOAL! REAL MADRID 3-0 Almeria It really is game over now and maybe Esteban should do better with that strike. A cross from right to left finds Isco and the right back Nelson allows him to turn. His near post shot should have been saved. It definitely is game over now - Almeria take off their top goalscorer Rodri for a midfielder. 22:11 From Sportsmail\'s Pete Jenson at the Bernabeu Seven of Bale\'s 14 league goals have come with Cristiano Ronaldo not in the side. He\'s stepped up every time he\'s been needed to fill in for Real\'s top scorer 22:08 52mins: GOAL! REAL MADRID 2-0 Almeria Beautifully worked team goal and Angel Di Maria is at the heart of it again. He drivers forwards and plays a give and go with Benzema. The winger gives it again to the Frenchman who shifts the ball one more to find Gareth Bale. His shot is at Esteban but it\'s too hot for the goalkeeper to handle and it looks like game over. Doubled: Gareth Bale celebrates after making it 2-0 to Real Madird 22:07 51mins From a Real corner it\'s half cleared and falls to Modric on the edge, but his shot is well hit but always bending away from goal. 22:06 49mins Another corner for Almeria but again the delivery is poor. The last two have gone straight into Diego Lopez\'s hands. They balls in have to be better if Almeria want a chance of coming back. 22:03 47mins Fantastic dummy from Isco to get some space for the shot, though it\'s blocked and goes behind for a corner. Nothing comes from that. 22:02 46mins Ominous statistic for Almeria - Real have won all 18 previous games in which they\'ve been ahead at half-time this season. 22:01 SECOND HALF We\'re back at the Bernabeu, Almeria start with the ball. 21:46 HALF TIME: Real Madrid 1-0 Almeria Opener: Angel Di Maria scores the first goal of the game with a curling strike 21:46 45mins Pepe wins a header and the ball lands at Benzema\'s feet. He strikes from outside the box but drags the shot wide of the left post. 21:42 41mins To put Almeria\'s struggles into a nice stat, their top passer has completed just six of his 16 passes... Luka Modric has almost 40 successful passes. 21:40 41mins Bale goes close this time - on the right hand side he cuts inside, gives the defender a step over and strikes towards the near post. It flashes wide. 21:39 38mins An outrageous attempt from Angel Di Maria almost catches Esteban off guard! From a corner Di Maria spots the keeper off his line - he attempts a direct shot and it takes a flying save to keep the ball out. Really unlucky from the Argentine who has been the best player in this first half. 21:37 37mins Almeria are offering nothing going forward. They work hard to get the ball back but as soon as they have it they give it away again. 21:36 35mins Well, Gareth Bale scored plenty of free-kicks from that kind of range last season, but that was poor. He steps up, tries to get the ball up and down but the ball just keeps going up and up and up. 21:33 From Sportsmail\'s Pete Jenson at the Bernabeu The Almeria substitute Silva is their fourth choice centre-back. He\'s played just one game all season. It\'s going to be a long second half. 21:32 31mins A third corner of the game for Almeria but the delivery is to the far post and again goes beyond everyone. 21:28 28mins: GOAL! REAL MADRID 1-0 Almeria No chance for Esteban and Real Madrid take a deserved lead! Angel Di Maria picks the ball up on the right hand side, cuts inside and drives into the box. The Almeria goalkeeper who has been excellent up to this point can do nothing as he puts the ball right in the top corner. Almeria were down to 10 men as that goal went in. Mobbed: Angel di Maria celebrates with team-mates after scoring the opener 21:27 26mins Bale looks like he should score but the angle is too tight. A through-ball sets the Welshman off and he nips in to take it round Esteban, but the onrushing keeper does well. Despite going round him there\'s no angle for the shot. Narrow: Esteban does well to narrow the angle as Bale goes through on goal 21:25 25mins Another good chance for Benzema, though you can\'t fault him for that miss. Di Maria fires in a cross from the left and Benzema leaps well but can\'t keep his header down. 21:23 22mins Brilliant save from Esteban! The winger bursts into the box going past two defenders, and just next to the penalty spot Bale tries to give Esteban the eyes. He shapes to shoot to Eteban\'s right but atually goes to the left, and the former Sevilla stopper is equal to the task. Superb goalkeeping 21:21 20mins Illarramendi loses a shoe in passing the ball into Bale, but the Welshman and fires from about 20 yards and it\'s always rising. Little bit scruffy from Real in the last couple of minutes. Thwarted: Isco knocks the ball away from Barbosa 21:19 19mins Isco done brilliantly to create himself a bit of room on the edge of the box but he rather rushes his pass, firing the ball into an area where Benzema can\'t reach it. 21:18 18mins Slow and deliberate pace to Real Madrid\'s play at the moment. 21:14 14mins Almeria win themselves a corner but the delivery is terrible and it flies past everyone and out for a goal kick. 21:12 12mins Having said that it only seems a matter of time before Real Madrid score. Gareth Bale bursts down the left and finds Karim Benzema, who can only lift his shot over the top. You\'d expect better from a player of his quality. 21:12 10mins Almeria are just working their way back into it at the moment, enjoying a little bit more pressure. Especially down the right hand side. 21:09 8mins Another long range shot troubles Esteban! Di Maria takes a potshot from about 30 yards out which the keeper punches straight up. He\'s put under pressure by Bale who is - harshly - judged to have fouled the goalkeeper. It looks like it\'s going to be a busy night for him. Penalised: Gareth Bale is juged to have fouled Esteban 21:07 6mins Another good save from Esteban, as he pushes a shot away to his right. It was Di Maria cut inside and curling the ball into the bottom corner. 21:03 4mins A great strike from Angel Di Maria rattles the crossbar, so unlucky! Esteban was beaten all ends up by that shot. 21:02 2mins Early chance for Almeria! The visitors win a corner and it\'s a free header at the back post, but it goes way, way over the top. 21:01 KICK-OFF Real Madrid get us started at the Bernabeu. 20:57 From Sportsmail\'s Pete Jenson at the Bernabeu Big roar goes up at the Bernabeu to the news that Barcelona have lost. All Real Madrid need to do now is beat Almeria who Madrid beat 8-1 last time they met here. 20:50 Team news Real Madrid: Diego Lopez, Varane, Pepe, Coentrao, Benzema, Bale, Nacho, Modric, Di Maria, Isco, Illarramendi. Almeria: Esteban, Nelson, Torsiglieri, Hans, Mane, Verza, Corona, Tebar, Barbosa, Zongo, Rodri. Missing: Cristiano Ronaldo misses out tonight because of a thigh injury 20:48 Hello Good evening everyone, welcome to live coverage of Real Madrid from the Bernabeu. There\'s no Cristiano Ronaldo for the home side tonight, but they should have more than enough firepower to brush past Almeria. Team news to follow. {\"id\":\"2603110\",\"channel\":\"/sport\",\"pageUrl\":\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2603110/LIVE-Real-Madrid-v-Almeria-La-Liga.html\",\"status\":\"running\",\"greenBox\":{\"title\":\"REAL MADRID 4-0 ALMERIA - FT\",\"body\":\"<p><font style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\"><strong>Real Madrid:</strong> Diego Lopez, Varane, Pepe, Coentrao (Llorente 743), Benzema, Bale (Morata 70), Nacho, Modric, Di Maria (Casemiro 64), Isco, Illarramendi.</font></p>\\n<p><font style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\"><strong>Goals:</strong> Di Maria 28, Bale 52, Isco 56, Morata 85.</font></p>\\n<p><font style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\"><strong>Almeria:</strong> Esteban, Nelson, Torsiglieri, Hans, Mane, Verza, Corona, Tebar, Barbosa, Zongo, Rodri.<br /></font></p>\"},\"modifiedOrder\":10} 0 0  Share or comment on this article','\n<p class=\"author-section\">By <a class=\"author\" href=\"/home/search.html?s=&amp;authornamef=Tom+Sheen\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tom Sheen</a> <span class=\"follow-author\"> <a class=\"twitter-follow-button twitter-follow-author\" data-show-count=\"false\" href=\"https://twitter.com/@Tom_Sheen\">Follow @@Tom_Sheen</a> </span> </p>\n<p class=\"byline-section\"><span class=\"article-timestamp article-timestamp-published\"> <span class=\"article-timestamp-label\">Published:</span> 06:12 EST, 12 April 2014 </span> | <span class=\"article-timestamp article-timestamp-updated\"> <span class=\"article-timestamp-label\">Updated:</span> 07:08 EST, 12 April 2014 </span> </p>\n<div id=\"articleIconLinksContainer\"> <ul> <li class=\"share-facebook\" onclick=\"postToFB(\'top\'); return false;\"></li> <li class=\"share-twitter\" onclick=\"postToTWTTR(\'top\'); return false;\"></li> <li class=\"share-pinterest\" onclick=\"postToPinterest(\'top\'); return false;\"></li> <li class=\"share-gplus\"> <span class=\"g-interactivepost\" data-calltoactionlabel=\"VIEW\" data-calltoactionurl=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2603110/LIVE-Real-Madrid-v-Almeria-La-Liga.html\" data-clientid=\"746589970956-e10ciaf67a1id9ggu75ph3ds0sthn7j6.apps.googleusercontent.com\" data-contentdeeplinkid=\"/pages\" data-contenturl=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2603110/LIVE-Real-Madrid-v-Almeria-La-Liga.html\" data-cookiepolicy=\"single_host_origin\" data-prefilltext=\"LIVE - Real Madrid v Almeria: Follow all the action from the Bernabeu as Los Blancos look to draw level with city rivals Atletico\"> <a onclick=\'postToGPlus(\"top\"); return false;\'></a> </span> </li> <li class=\"share-icons\" id=\"shareLinkTop\"> <a class=\"js-sl share-link\" href=\"#socialLinks\"> </a> </li> </ul> <a class=\"comments-count home\" href=\"/sport/football/article-2603110/LIVE-Real-Madrid-v-Almeria-La-Liga.html#comments\"> <span></span> <p class=\"count-number\">3</p> <p class=\"count-text\">View <br/> comments</p> </a> </div>\n<div class=\"floatRHS art-ins sport\"><h3 class=\"wocc\"><b>REAL MADRID V ALMERIA</b><br/></h3><div class=\"ins cleared xolcc bdrcc\"><p><font style=\"font-size: 1.2em;\">Santiago Bernabeu, Madrid</font><br/><font style=\"font-size: 1.2em;\">La Liga<br/><i>(Kick-off 9pm BST)</i><br/></font></p></div></div>\n<font style=\"font-size:1.2em;\"><br/></font>\n<p><font style=\"font-size:1.2em;\">Real Madrid may be in the semi-finals of the Champions League, but they will be looking to get their La Liga campaign back on track at the Bernabeu.</font></p>\n<p><font style=\"font-size:1.2em;\">A win against Almeria would put Carlo Ancelotti\'s men level on points with their city rivals Atletico, who led the way in Spain coming into the weekend.</font></p>\n<p><font style=\"font-size:1.2em;\">Real Madrid will also have one eye on their Copa del Rey final against Barcelona at the Mestalla on Wednesday.</font></p>\n<div class=\"pageBreak\"> </div>\n<div class=\"moduleFull\"> <div class=\"home item html_snippet_module\"> <!-- Live commentary 2 --> <div data-app-version=\"3\" data-refresh-time=\"\" id=\"lc-commentary-container\"> <div class=\"lc-host-commentator cleared\"> <ul> <li> <img src=\"\"/> <b>Tom Sheen</b> <p>Host commentator</p> </li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-live-update\"> <span class=\"lc-manual-update\"> <span class=\"lc-commentary-newitems-info\"> <a class=\"lc-update-qty\" href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.showNewPosts()\"></a> </span> </span> <div class=\"onoffswitch\" id=\"lc-auto-refresh-switch\"> <input class=\"onoffswitch-checkbox\" id=\"lc-auto-refresh\" name=\"onoffswitch\" type=\"checkbox\"/> <label class=\"onoffswitch-label\" for=\"lc-auto-refresh\"> <div class=\"onoffswitch-inner\"></div> <div class=\"onoffswitch-switch\"></div> </label> </div> <!--[if (IE)|(lt IE 9)]> <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"onoffswitch\" class=\"lc-IE78\" id=\"lc-auto-refresh\"> <![endif]--> <label class=\"lc-auto-update\" for=\"lc-auto-refresh\">Auto-update</label> </div> <div id=\"lc-commentary-posts\"><div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-46\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/match/60x60_ft.png\"/> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/champ_league/60x60_real_madrid.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:48 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>FULL TIME: Real Madrid 4-0 Almeria</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Real Madrid move into second place in La Liga. They are now level on points with their cross town rivals - and have a superior goal difference - but are second due to the head-to-head record.</p> <p>Diego Simeone\'s men play Getafe tomorrow night.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'46\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'46\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-45\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:45 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>89mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Real Madrid fans starting to file out of the Bernabeu.</p> <p>Isco should have sent them on their way with a goal there as well. Benzema turned and found the former Malaga man in the box but he gets his shot all wrong and it dribbles straight into Esteban\'s arms.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'45\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'45\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-44\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/match/60x60_goal.png\"/> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/champ_league/60x60_real_madrid.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:40 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>85mins: GOAL! REAL MADRID 4-0 Almeria</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Lovely pass and a lovely finish to put the icing on Real Madrid\'s cake.</p> <p>Illarramendi lofts a pass to <strong>Morata</strong> - half of the Almeria defence tries to play offside, the other doesn\'t - and Morata lets the ball bounce once before stroking the ball into the roof of the net, neat finish.</p> </div> <img class=\"lc-post-image\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/12/1397339219766_lc_galleryImage_Real_Madrid_s_forward_Alv.JPG\"/> <b class=\"lc-image-caption\">Finishing touch: Alvaro Morata makes it 4-0 to Real Madrid with a smart finish</b> <div class=\"lc-clear\"></div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'44\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'44\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-43\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:38 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>81mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Terrible miss from Benzema, he\'s had some really good chances tonight. Modric\'s free-kick hits the wall, it falls to Morata who cleverly back-heels to Benzema.</p> <p>Rather than the cool and calm finish we are used to seeing from him, he snatches at it, hitting the ball as hard as he can. It, of course, flies over the top.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'43\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'43\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-42\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:35 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>78mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Real Madrid are claiming for a penalty, but I think that would have been harsh had it been given.</p> <p>Isco scoops a clever ball over the top to Morata and the defender doesn\'t get too much of the ball but the substitute definitely tries to make the most of the contact, going down rather too easily.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'42\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'42\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-41\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:31 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>75mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Another good chance for Benzema. Morata is set off down the left, he cuts back inside ad curls a ball into the striker, who takes it first time but drags the volley just wide.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'41\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'41\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-40\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/match/60x60_substitution.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:29 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>73mins: Real Mdrid sub</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Fabio Coentrao is replaced by another youngster Diego Llorente.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'40\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'40\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-39\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/match/60x60_substitution.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:25 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>70mins: Real Madrid sub</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Gareth Bale is replaced by Real youngster Alvaro Morata.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'39\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'39\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-38\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:25 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>68mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Sustained pressure from Real Madrid and a couple of close calls but they can\'t quite turn the ball into the net.</p> <p>Coentrao fires across the box and then it comes the other way from Isco.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'38\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'38\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-37\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:21 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>65mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Diego Lopez is finally called into action and makes a really good save.</p> <p>From the free-kick the big goalkeeper gets down to his left smartly.</p> </div> <img class=\"lc-post-image\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/12/1397338606245_lc_galleryImage_Real_Madrid_s_midfielder_.JPG\"/> <b class=\"lc-image-caption\">Game over: Isco adds Real Madrid\'s third and ends the contest</b> <div class=\"lc-clear\"></div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'37\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'37\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-36\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/match/60x60_substitution.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:20 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>64mins: Real Madrid sub</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Angel di Maria is replaced by Casemiro. Excellent performance from the Argentine.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'36\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'36\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-35\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:16 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>60mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Esteban goes some way to making up for that earlier miss, with a good save from marauding left back Fabio Coentrao.</p> <p>The overlapping full back had options but decides to shoot through the goalkeeper\'s legs, Esteban gets just enough on it to keep him out.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'35\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'35\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-34\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/match/60x60_goal.png\"/> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/champ_league/60x60_real_madrid.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:11 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>56mins: GOAL! REAL MADRID 3-0 Almeria</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>It really is game over now and maybe Esteban should do better with that strike.</p> <p>A cross from right to left finds <strong>Isco </strong>and the right back Nelson allows him to turn. His near post shot should have been saved.</p> <p>It definitely is game over now - Almeria take off their top goalscorer Rodri for a midfielder.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'34\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'34\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-33\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/champ_league/60x60_real_madrid.png\"/> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:11 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>From Sportsmail\'s Pete Jenson at the Bernabeu</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p><em>Seven of Bale\'s 14 league goals have come with Cristiano Ronaldo not in the side. He\'s stepped up every time he\'s been needed to fill in for Real\'s top scorer</em></p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'33\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'33\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-32\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/match/60x60_goal.png\"/> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/champ_league/60x60_real_madrid.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:08 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>52mins: GOAL! REAL MADRID 2-0 Almeria</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Beautifully worked team goal and Angel Di Maria is at the heart of it again.</p> <p>He drivers forwards and plays a give and go with Benzema. The winger gives it again to the Frenchman who shifts the ball one more to find <strong>Gareth Bale</strong>.</p> <p>His shot is at Esteban but it\'s too hot for the goalkeeper to handle and it looks like game over.</p> </div> <img class=\"lc-post-image\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/12/1397337469798_lc_galleryImage_Real_Madrid_s_Welsh_forwa.JPG\"/> <b class=\"lc-image-caption\">Doubled: Gareth Bale celebrates after making it 2-0 to Real Madird</b> <div class=\"lc-clear\"></div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'32\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'32\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-31\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:07 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>51mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>From a Real corner it\'s half cleared and falls to Modric on the edge, but his shot is well hit but always bending away from goal.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'31\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'31\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-30\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:06 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>49mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Another corner for Almeria but again the delivery is poor. The last two have gone straight into Diego Lopez\'s hands.</p> <p>They balls in have to be better if Almeria want a chance of coming back.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'30\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'30\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-29\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:03 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>47mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Fantastic dummy from Isco to get some space for the shot, though it\'s blocked and goes behind for a corner.</p> <p>Nothing comes from that.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'29\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'29\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-28\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:02 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>46mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Ominous statistic for Almeria - Real have won all 18 previous games in which they\'ve been ahead at half-time this season.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'28\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'28\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-27\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/match/60x60_ko.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">22:01 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>SECOND HALF</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>We\'re back at the Bernabeu, Almeria start with the ball.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'27\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'27\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-26\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/match/60x60_ht.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:46 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>HALF TIME: Real Madrid 1-0 Almeria</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> </div> <img class=\"lc-post-image\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/12/1397336619846_lc_galleryImage_Real_s_Angel_Di_Maria_rig.JPG\"/> <b class=\"lc-image-caption\">Opener: Angel Di Maria scores the first goal of the game with a curling strike</b> <div class=\"lc-clear\"></div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'26\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'26\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-25\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:46 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>45mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Pepe wins a header and the ball lands at Benzema\'s feet. He strikes from outside the box but drags the shot wide of the left post.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'25\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'25\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-24\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:42 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>41mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>To put Almeria\'s struggles into a nice stat, their top passer has completed just six of his 16 passes... Luka Modric has almost 40 successful passes.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'24\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'24\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-23\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:40 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>41mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Bale goes close this time - on the right hand side he cuts inside, gives the defender a step over and strikes towards the near post.</p> <p>It flashes wide.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'23\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'23\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-22\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:39 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>38mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>An outrageous attempt from Angel Di Maria almost catches Esteban off guard!</p> <p>From a corner Di Maria spots the keeper off his line - he attempts a direct shot and it takes a flying save to keep the ball out.</p> <p>Really unlucky from the Argentine who has been the best player in this first half.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'22\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'22\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-21\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:37 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>37mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Almeria are offering nothing going forward. They work hard to get the ball back but as soon as they have it they give it away again.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'21\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'21\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-20\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:36 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>35mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Well, Gareth Bale scored plenty of free-kicks from that kind of range last season, but that was poor.</p> <p>He steps up, tries to get the ball up and down but the ball just keeps going up and up and up.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'20\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'20\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-19\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/champ_league/60x60_real_madrid.png\"/> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:33 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>From Sportsmail\'s Pete Jenson at the Bernabeu</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p><em>The Almeria substitute Silva is their fourth choice centre-back. He\'s played just one game all season. It\'s going to be a long second half.</em></p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'19\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'19\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-18\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:32 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>31mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>A third corner of the game for Almeria but the delivery is to the far post and again goes beyond everyone.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'18\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'18\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-17\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/match/60x60_goal.png\"/> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/champ_league/60x60_real_madrid.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:28 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>28mins: GOAL! REAL MADRID 1-0 Almeria</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>No chance for Esteban and Real Madrid take a deserved lead! <strong>Angel Di Maria</strong> picks the ball up on the right hand side, cuts inside and drives into the box.</p> <p>The Almeria goalkeeper who has been excellent up to this point can do nothing as he puts the ball right in the top corner.</p> <p>Almeria were down to 10 men as that goal went in.</p> </div> <img class=\"lc-post-image\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/12/1397335199218_lc_galleryImage_Real_Madrid_s_Argentinian.JPG\"/> <b class=\"lc-image-caption\">Mobbed: Angel di Maria celebrates with team-mates after scoring the opener</b> <div class=\"lc-clear\"></div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'17\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'17\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-16\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:27 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>26mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Bale looks like he should score but the angle is too tight. A through-ball sets the Welshman off and he nips in to take it round Esteban, but the onrushing keeper does well.</p> <p>Despite going round him there\'s no angle for the shot.</p> </div> <img class=\"lc-post-image\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/12/1397334883650_lc_galleryImage_Real_Madrid_s_Welsh_forwa.JPG\"/> <b class=\"lc-image-caption\">Narrow: Esteban does well to narrow the angle as Bale goes through on goal</b> <div class=\"lc-clear\"></div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'16\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'16\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-15\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:25 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>25mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Another good chance for Benzema, though you can\'t fault him for that miss.</p> <p>Di Maria fires in a cross from the left and Benzema leaps well but can\'t keep his header down.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'15\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'15\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-14\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:23 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>22mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Brilliant save from Esteban!</p> <p>The winger bursts into the box going past two defenders, and just next to the penalty spot Bale tries to give Esteban the eyes.</p> <p>He shapes to shoot to Eteban\'s right but atually goes to the left, and the former Sevilla stopper is equal to the task.</p> <p>Superb goalkeeping</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'14\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'14\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-13\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:21 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>20mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Illarramendi loses a shoe in passing the ball into Bale, but the Welshman and fires from about 20 yards and it\'s always rising.</p> <p>Little bit scruffy from Real in the last couple of minutes.</p> </div> <img class=\"lc-post-image\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/12/1397334646266_lc_galleryImage_Real_Madrid_s_midfielder_.JPG\"/> <b class=\"lc-image-caption\">Thwarted: Isco knocks the ball away from Barbosa</b> <div class=\"lc-clear\"></div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'13\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'13\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-12\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:19 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>19mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Isco done brilliantly to create himself a bit of room on the edge of the box but he rather rushes his pass, firing the ball into an area where Benzema can\'t reach it.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'12\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'12\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-11\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:18 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>18mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Slow and deliberate pace to Real Madrid\'s play at the moment.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'11\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'11\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-10\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:14 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>14mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Almeria win themselves a corner but the delivery is terrible and it flies past everyone and out for a goal kick.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'10\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'10\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-9\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:12 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>12mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Having said that it only seems a matter of time before Real Madrid score.</p> <p>Gareth Bale bursts down the left and finds Karim Benzema, who can only lift his shot over the top. You\'d expect better from a player of his quality.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'9\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'9\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-8\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:12 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>10mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Almeria are just working their way back into it at the moment, enjoying a little bit more pressure. Especially down the right hand side.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'8\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'8\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-7\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:09 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>8mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Another long range shot troubles Esteban!</p> <p>Di Maria takes a potshot from about 30 yards out which the keeper punches straight up. He\'s put under pressure by Bale who is - harshly - judged to have fouled the goalkeeper.</p> <p>It looks like it\'s going to be a busy night for him.</p> </div> <img class=\"lc-post-image\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/12/1397334361924_lc_galleryImage_Real_Madrid_s_Welsh_forwa.JPG\"/> <b class=\"lc-image-caption\">Penalised: Gareth Bale is juged to have fouled Esteban</b> <div class=\"lc-clear\"></div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'7\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'7\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-6\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:07 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>6mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Another good save from Esteban, as he pushes a shot away to his right. It was Di Maria cut inside and curling the ball into the bottom corner.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'6\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'6\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-5\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:03 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>4mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>A great strike from Angel Di Maria rattles the crossbar, so unlucky!</p> <p>Esteban was beaten all ends up by that shot.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'5\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'5\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-4\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:02 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>2mins</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Early chance for Almeria!</p> <p>The visitors win a corner and it\'s a free header at the back post, but it goes way, way over the top.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'4\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'4\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-3\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/champ_league/60x60_real_madrid.png\"/> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">21:01 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>KICK-OFF</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Real Madrid get us started at the Bernabeu.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'3\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'3\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-2\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/champ_league/60x60_real_madrid.png\"/> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">20:57 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>From Sportsmail\'s Pete Jenson at the Bernabeu</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p><em>Big roar goes up at the Bernabeu to the news that Barcelona have lost. All Real Madrid need to do now is beat Almeria who Madrid beat 8-1 last time they met here.</em></p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'2\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'2\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-1\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/champ_league/60x60_real_madrid.png\"/> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">20:50 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>Team news</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p><strong>Real Madrid: </strong>Diego Lopez, Varane, Pepe, Coentrao, Benzema, Bale, Nacho, Modric, Di Maria, Isco, Illarramendi.</p> <p><strong>Almeria:</strong> Esteban, Nelson, Torsiglieri, Hans, Mane, Verza, Corona, Tebar, Barbosa, Zongo, Rodri.</p> </div> <img class=\"lc-post-image\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/12/1397334258145_lc_galleryImage_DORTMUND_GERMANY_APRIL_08.JPG\"/> <b class=\"lc-image-caption\">Missing: Cristiano Ronaldo misses out tonight because of a thigh injury</b> <div class=\"lc-clear\"></div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'1\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'1\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"lc-commentary-post cleared\" id=\"lc-id-0\"> <div class=\"lc-icons\"> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/champ_league/60x60_real_madrid.png\"/> <img class=\"lc-icon\" src=\"http://i.mol.im/i/furniture/live_commentary/football_icons/flags/60x60_spain.png\"/> <div class=\"lc-post-time\">20:48 </div> </div> <div class=\"lc-title-container\"> <span><b>Hello</b></span> </div> <div class=\"lc-post-body\"> <p>Good evening everyone, welcome to live coverage of Real Madrid from the Bernabeu.</p> <p>There\'s no Cristiano Ronaldo for the home side tonight, but they should have more than enough firepower to brush past Almeria.</p> <p>Team news to follow.</p> </div> <ul class=\"lc-social\"> <li class=\"lc-facebook\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToFB, \'0\', \'facebook\')\"></span></li> <li class=\"lc-twitter\"><span onclick=\"window.LiveCommentary.socialShare(postToTWTTR, \'0\', \'twitter\', window.twitterVia)\"></span></li> </ul> </div> </div> <span id=\"lc-metadata\" style=\"display:none\">{\"id\":\"2603110\",\"channel\":\"/sport\",\"pageUrl\":\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2603110/LIVE-Real-Madrid-v-Almeria-La-Liga.html\",\"status\":\"running\",\"greenBox\":{\"title\":\"REAL MADRID 4-0 ALMERIA - FT\",\"body\":\"&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Real Madrid:&lt;/strong&gt; Diego Lopez, Varane, Pepe, Coentrao (Llorente 743), Benzema, Bale (Morata 70), Nacho, Modric, Di Maria (Casemiro 64), Isco, Illarramendi.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Goals:&lt;/strong&gt; Di Maria 28, Bale 52, Isco 56, Morata 85.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Almeria:&lt;/strong&gt; Esteban, Nelson, Torsiglieri, Hans, Mane, Verza, Corona, Tebar, Barbosa, Zongo, Rodri.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\"},\"modifiedOrder\":10}</span> <span id=\"lc-latest-modification-time\" style=\"display:none\">0</span> <span id=\"lc-latest-modification-order\" style=\"display:none\">0</span> <link href=\"http://livecommentary.dailymail.co.uk/apps/livecommentary_public/css/commentary.css?cb=1395314270\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/> <link href=\"http://livecommentary.dailymail.co.uk/apps/livecommentary_public/css/sport/commentary.css?cb=1395314270\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/> </div> <!-- FOR IE7 and below - must include before JSON.parse --> </div> </div>\n<div class=\"clear\"> </div>\n<div class=\"column-content cleared\"> <div class=\"shareArticles\"> <h3 class=\"social-links-title\">Share or comment on this article</h3> <div class=\"social-links cleared\" id=\"socialLinks\"> <ul class=\"bigLinks sc-icns cleared\"> <li class=\"facebook\"> <a class=\"js-tl\" onclick=\'postToFB(\"bottom\"); return false;\' rel=\"nofollow\"></a> </li> <li class=\"twitter\"> <a class=\"js-tl\" onclick=\"postToTWTTR(\'bottom\'); return false;\" rel=\"nofollow\"></a> </li> <li class=\"pinterest\"> <a class=\"js-tl\" onclick=\"postToPinterest(\'bottom\'); return false;\" rel=\"nofollow\"></a> </li> <li class=\"googleplus\"> <span class=\"g-interactivepost\" data-calltoactionlabel=\"VIEW\" data-calltoactionurl=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2603110/LIVE-Real-Madrid-v-Almeria-La-Liga.html\" data-clientid=\"746589970956-e10ciaf67a1id9ggu75ph3ds0sthn7j6.apps.googleusercontent.com\" data-contentdeeplinkid=\"/pages\" data-contenturl=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2603110/LIVE-Real-Madrid-v-Almeria-La-Liga.html\" data-cookiepolicy=\"single_host_origin\" data-prefilltext=\"LIVE - Real Madrid v Almeria: Follow all the action from the Bernabeu as Los Blancos look to draw level with city rivals Atletico\"> <a class=\"js-tl\" onclick=\"postToGPlus(\'bottom\');\" rel=\"nofollow\"></a> </span> </li> <li class=\"email\"> <a class=\"js-tl\" href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2603110/emailArticle.html\" onclick=\"emailArticle(\'bottom\');\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_new\" title=\"Email to a friend\"> </a> </li> <li class=\"share\" id=\"shareLinkBottom\"> <a class=\"js-sl share-link\" href=\"#socialLinks\"> </a> </li> <li class=\"add-comment\" id=\"addCommentButton\"> <a href=\"#newcomment\" rel=\"nofollow\"> </a> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div>','http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/12/article-2603110-1D0C287900000578-359_1024x615_large.jpg',NULL,'2014-04-12 16:58:00','2014-04-12 14:08:19'),(38,'b7cb3760074569eda4165fd98a9893632147cfccdf5a9cf1c2fe73ecd7c42efc','dailymail',NULL,'Only THREE Premier League clubs have adequate wheelchair facilities','http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2603127/Only-THREE-Premier-League-clubs-adequate-wheelchair-facilities.html',' By David Kent Published: 06:40 EST, 12 April 2014 | Updated: 06:40 EST, 12 April 2014 11 shares 5 View comments The Government is putting more pressure on football clubs to make their grounds user-friendly for disabled fans after a report discovered several were failing to cater for less able-bodied supporters. Minister for disabled people, Mike Penning MP, said he would look to prosecute clubs that failed to meet criteria designed to welcome supporters. A BBC report last month revealed that just three Premier League stadiums - Swansea\'s Liberty Stadium, St Mary\'s in Southampton, and the Cardiff City Stadium - provide the required number of wheelchair spaces.  Not good enough; Fulham\'s Craven Cottage has the fewest wheelchair spaces provided as a percentage  More... JAMIE CARRAGHER: Hillsborough - every child must be told why games kick off seven minutes late this weekend Van Gaal lined up to be next Man United boss as Moyes faces axe in summer after disastrous first season at Old Trafford FA Cup win can bring back glory days for barren Arsenal, says Oxlade-Chamberlain Chelsea to face Courtois as UEFA tell Blues they can\'t stop Atletico keeper playing Roar us to title! We\'ll unleash power of Anfield against City, says Liverpool boss Rodgers CHARLES SALE: Liverpool lead the way in selling signed shirts... Suarez\'s is yours for just £3,000 Fulham\'s Craven Cottage has the fewest wheelchair spaces provided as a percentage of Accessible Stadia Guide recommendations, the BBC investigation found. Tory MP for Hemel Hempstead Mr Penning said the report \'named and shamed\' poorly performing clubs and he had written to all Football League teams to remind them of their responsibilities. Speaking on the BBC\'s Breakfast programme today, the Tottenham fan said: \'Enough is enough. I\'m a football fan and my club, Spurs, is right at the bottom of this league table (on disability provision). \'There\'s so much money in the Football League, why can\'t (disabled) fans go and see their games the same way you and I can? \'What I\'ve said is \"sort your act out\". Sadly if you don\'t, the legislation is there for me to take prosecutions if I need to.\'  Small amount: Crystal Palace\'s Selhurst Park is one of only three Premier League grounds to meet standards  The Accessible Stadia Guide is a \'good practice guide\' for sporting facilities to meet the needs of disabled spectators and other users. It sets out minimum standards all new grounds have to meet in the provision, location and quality of facilities for disabled fans. Since the implementation of the Equality Act in 2010, and legislation dating back to 1995, it has been illegal for service providers, including football clubs, to treat disabled people less favourably than other customers. Mr Penning said he has also written to the Football Association chairman, former BBC director-general Greg Dyke, and described the situation.  Crackdown: MP Mike Penning said he would look to prosecute clubs that failed to meet criteria  The MP said: \'It\'s not just about wheelchair access. You can get wheelchair access in but if you just plant them around the edge of the game, they don\'t feel part of the game, they don\'t feel part of the atmosphere. \'I want to build on the legacy from the Paralympics and football clubs need to use a piece of their loose change.\' In a statement, the Premier League said: \'All Premier League clubs have arrangements in place to provide access and facilities for disabled fans. The highest standards of access are generally at clubs with new grounds but all clubs, even those working within the constraints of older stadia, work hard to make sure that disabled fans can attend matches and enjoy their football. \'The Accessible Stadia Guide sets out agreed standards to be achieved when new grounds are designed or existing grounds rebuilt, however all clubs use those standards to assess existing provisions and guide them on how to make improvements. \'Particular attention is given to achieving stadium management solutions that make the best of the constraints and opportunities inherent in each stadium. This includes working with the fans to arrive at solutions that work for them, and providing special training for stewards and staff to ensure that appropriate assistance is given.\'   More... JAMIE CARRAGHER: Hillsborough - every child must be told why games kick off seven minutes late this weekend Van Gaal lined up to be next Man United boss as Moyes faces axe in summer after disastrous first season at Old Trafford FA Cup win can bring back glory days for barren Arsenal, says Oxlade-Chamberlain Chelsea to face Courtois as UEFA tell Blues they can\'t stop Atletico keeper playing Roar us to title! We\'ll unleash power of Anfield against City, says Liverpool boss Rodgers CHARLES SALE: Liverpool lead the way in selling signed shirts... Suarez\'s is yours for just £3,000  Share or comment on this article 11shares','\n<p class=\"author-section\">By <a class=\"author\" href=\"/home/search.html?s=&amp;authornamef=David+Kent\" rel=\"nofollow\">David Kent</a> </p>\n<p class=\"byline-section\"><span class=\"article-timestamp article-timestamp-published\"> <span class=\"article-timestamp-label\">Published:</span> 06:40 EST, 12 April 2014 </span> | <span class=\"article-timestamp article-timestamp-updated\"> <span class=\"article-timestamp-label\">Updated:</span> 06:40 EST, 12 April 2014 </span> </p>\n<div id=\"articleIconLinksContainer\"> <ul> <li class=\"share-facebook\" onclick=\"postToFB(\'top\'); return false;\"></li> <li class=\"share-twitter\" onclick