s=\"googleplus\"> <span class=\"g-interactivepost\" data-calltoactionlabel=\"VIEW\" data-calltoactionurl=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2602639/EXCLUSIVE-City-axe-academy-chief-Sellars-fears-homegrown-quota-grow.html\" data-clientid=\"746589970956-e10ciaf67a1id9ggu75ph3ds0sthn7j6.apps.googleusercontent.com\" data-contentdeeplinkid=\"/pages\" data-contenturl=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2602639/EXCLUSIVE-City-axe-academy-chief-Sellars-fears-homegrown-quota-grow.html\" data-cookiepolicy=\"single_host_origin\" data-prefilltext=\"EXCLUSIVE: Sellars axed from Man City academy role as fears over homegrown quota grow\"> <a class=\"js-tl\" onclick=\"postToGPlus(\'bottom\');\" rel=\"nofollow\"></a> </span> </li> <li class=\"email\"> <a class=\"js-tl\" href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2602639/emailArticle.html\" onclick=\"emailArticle(\'bottom\');\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_new\" title=\"Email to a friend\"> </a> </li> <li class=\"share\" id=\"shareLinkBottom\"> <a class=\"js-sl share-link\" href=\"#socialLinks\"> </a> </li> <li class=\"social-stats social-stats-pipe\" id=\"shareCountBottom\"> <div> <div class=\"shares_count\">49</div><div class=\"shares_text\">shares</div> </div> </li> <li class=\"add-comment\" id=\"addCommentButton\"> <a href=\"#newcomment\" rel=\"nofollow\"> </a> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div>','http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/11/article-2602639-1D09306700000578-884_1024x615_large.jpg',NULL,'2014-04-12 16:58:25','2014-04-11 19:00:53'),(77,'dd7732fad2e81168639c0e808f915b4584659a37072e53605b436cfee0475c20','dailymail',NULL,'Welbeck and Cleverley pictured dancing in the street... hours after returning from United\'s Champions League exit','http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2602434/Welbeck-Cleverley-seen-dancing-street-early-hours-The-day-United-crashed-Champions-League.html',' By Graeme Yorke Published: 07:05 EST, 11 April 2014 | Updated: 11:25 EST, 11 April 2014 1,436 shares 511 View comments Manchester United players Danny Welbeck and Tom Cleverley have been pictured dancing in the street after the club were knocked out of the Champions League by Bayern Munich. England striker Welbeck, 23, and his team-mate Cleverley, 24, partied in Manchester city centre until 3am today after United crashed out of Europe following the 4-2 aggregate defeat by the German side on Wednesday night. Sportsmail understands that United flew home on Thursday ahead of a 10-day break in action and the players were given some time off before their trip to Everton on Sunday April 20. VIDEO Scroll down for Moyes\' passionate defence of the much maligned Cleverley, in March Dancing in the street: Manchester United stars Danny Welbeck and Tom Cleverley (left) out on the town in Manchester city centre at 3.20am today... hours after United arrived back from Germany   Dan the man: Welbeck (centre) holds back a pal as the United star chats to a girl in the street    Party boys: Welbeck chats to a girl (left) as Cleverley (right) shows off his moves in the street   Striking pair: England centre forward Welbeck (left) with a girl outside the back of the Sakura nightspot         Painting the town red: Cleverley (left) was pictured here enjoying himself on a night out in Manchester\'s Deansgate Locks area More... Moyes faces uncertain future... with up to 10 United stars heading for Old Trafford exit We went for Fergie! Newcastle tried to sign United great after Keegan, admits Shepherd Chelsea land Atletico Madrid in semi-finals of the Champions League Liverpool vs Man City is THE match to decide destination of the Premier League title... but will it live up to these classics? MATCH ZONE: Bayern Munich 3-1 (Agg: 4-2) Manchester United The England pair were joined by winger Ashley Young, according to the Manchester Evening News, for the night which started at a popular nightspot called Neighbourhood before moving on to Sakura at the city\'s Deansgate Locks. Welbeck was replaced after 81 minutes by Adnan Januzaj at the Allianz Arena. Young was an unused substitute but Cleverley was not part of the quarter-final, second leg squad. United lost 3-1 on the night despite Patrice Evra\'s thunderbolt opener. Eyewitnesses report Young getting into a taxi before Welbeck emerged from the rear entrance of Sakura. David Moyes makes a passionate defence of Tom Cleverley  Taxi! United midfielder Cleverley jigs around a mini-cab as a girl looks to leave the Deansgate Locks area   Good night: Cleverley bids the girl farewell after his night out with Welbeck and Ashley Young. Young had left the club earlier in a taxi   Street party: Welbeck (hidden, back right) and his friends were in boisterous mood despite United\'s Euro exit   Other half: Tom Cleverley\'s fiance Georgina Dorsett photographed out in Cheshire on Friday afternoon  He was then joined by Cleverley and the pair were both seen dancing in front of friends. One onlooker told the MEN: \'It is amazing. They were laughing and dancing and looked to be having a real good night. \'It is surprising after their defeat on Wednesday but it looked like they had fun.\' There is no suggestion that the players had broken any club curfew as there is no first-team match for more than a week. Manchester United declined to comment on the situation.  Getting stuck in: Welbeck challenges Bayern Munich\'s Thomas Muller (right) during Wednesday\'s clash    More... Moyes faces uncertain future... with up to 10 United stars heading for Old Trafford exit We went for Fergie! Newcastle tried to sign United great after Keegan, admits Shepherd Chelsea land Atletico Madrid in semi-finals of the Champions League Liverpool vs Man City is THE match to decide destination of the Premier League title... but will it live up to these classics? MATCH ZONE: Bayern Munich 3-1 (Agg: 4-2) Manchester United  Share or comment on this article 1.4kshares','\n<p class=\"author-section\">By <a class=\"author\" href=\"/home/search.html?s=&amp;authornamef=Graeme+Yorke\" rel=\"nofollow\">Graeme Yorke</a> </p>\n<p class=\"byline-section\"><span class=\"article-timestamp article-timestamp-published\"> <span class=\"article-timestamp-label\">Published:</span> 07:05 EST, 11 April 2014 </span> | <span class=\"article-timestamp article-timestamp-updated\"> <span class=\"article-timestamp-label\">Updated:</span> 11:25 EST, 11 April 2014 </span> </p>\n<div id=\"articleIconLinksContainer\"> <ul> <li class=\"share-facebook\" onclick=\"postToFB(\'top\'); return false;\"></li> <li class=\"share-twitter\" onclick=\"postToTWTTR(\'top\'); return false;\"></li> <li class=\"share-pinterest\" onclick=\"postToPinterest(\'top\'); return false;\"></li> <li class=\"share-gplus\"> <span class=\"g-interactivepost\" data-calltoactionlabel=\"VIEW\" data-calltoactionurl=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2602434/Welbeck-Cleverley-seen-dancing-street-early-hours-The-day-United-crashed-Champions-League.html\" data-clientid=\"746589970956-e10ciaf67a1id9ggu75ph3ds0sthn7j6.apps.googleusercontent.com\" data-contentdeeplinkid=\"/pages\" data-contenturl=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2602434/Welbeck-Cleverley-seen-dancing-street-early-hours-The-day-United-crashed-Champions-League.html\" data-cookiepolicy=\"single_host_origin\" data-prefilltext=\"Welbeck and Cleverley pictured dancing in the street... hours after returning from United\'s Champions League exit\"> <a onclick=\'postToGPlus(\"top\"); return false;\'></a> </span> </li> <li class=\"share-icons\" id=\"shareLinkTop\"> <a class=\"js-sl share-link\" href=\"#socialLinks\"> </a> </li> </ul> <div class=\"share-count\"> <b> 1,436</b> <span>shares</span> </div> <a class=\"comments-count home\" href=\"/sport/football/article-2602434/Welbeck-Cleverley-seen-dancing-street-early-hours-The-day-United-crashed-Champions-League.html#comments\"> <span></span> <p class=\"count-number\">511</p> <p class=\"count-text\">View <br/> comments</p> </a> </di